# Project Rules

- Follow clean architecture (routers → services → models)
- Never mix DB logic inside routers
- Use async functions everywhere
- Use dependency injection (FastAPI Depends)
- Validate all inputs with Pydantic
- Use environment variables via .env
- Always write modular, reusable code
- Follow REST API conventions
- Handle errors with proper HTTP status codes
Always assume:
- Postgres and Redis run in Docker containers
- Services are managed via docker-compose
- Service names:
  - postgres
  - redis
- Internal Docker networking may use:
  - postgres:5432
  - redis:6379